text:
Arizona Spring Training Ticket Sales 
When do the Los Angeles Angels of Anaheim Spring Training tickets go on sale? December 2, 2016 at 10 a.m. local time online and by phone. February 11, 2017 at 9 a.m. at the Box Office. 
When do the Oakland Athletics Spring Training tickets go on sale? November 15, 2016 at 10 a.m. and by phone to 877-493-2255. 
continue reading below our video Long-Haul Flight Survival Tips Schedule and ticket info for Oakland As Cactus League games 
When do the Milwaukee Brewers Spring Training tickets go on sale? Monday, December 5, 2016 at 8 a.m. online and by phone. The box office opens on February 6, 2017 at 9 a.m. 
When do the Chicago Cubs Spring Training tickets go on sale? January 7, 2017 at 10 a.m. online, by phone and at the Box Office. Schedule and ticket info for Chicago Cubs Cactus League games 
When do the Arizona Diamondbacks Spring Training tickets go on sale? January 7, 2017 at 10 a.m. online, at the box office at Salt River Fields at Talking Stick or by calling 1-888-490-0383. Schedule and ticket info for Arizona Diamondbacks Cactus League games 
When do the Los Angeles Dodgers Spring Training tickets go on sale? January 9, 2017 at 10 a.m. by phone and online. Box office opens January 30, 2017 at 10 a.m. 
When do the San Francisco Giants Spring Training tickets go on sale? January 12, 2017 at 10 a.m. online or by phone and at the Box Office. Schedule and ticket info for San Francisco Giants Cactus League games 
When do the Cleveland Indians Spring Training tickets go on sale? Thursday, December 1, 2016 at 10 a.m. online. Goodyear Ballpark Ticket Office opens January 14, 2017 at 10 a.m. Schedule and ticket info for Cleveland Indians Cactus League games 
When do the Seattle Mariners Spring Training tickets go on sale? December 10, 2016 at 9 a.m. online and by phone. The box office opens on January 28, 2017 at 10 a.m. Schedule and ticket info for Seattle Mariners Cactus League games

When do the Texas Rangers Spring Training tickets go on sale? December 10, 2016 at 8 a.m. online and by phone. The box office opens on January 7, 2017 at 7 a.m. Schedule and ticket info for Texas Rangers Cactus League games 
When do the Cincinnati Reds Spring Training tickets go on sale? Thursday, December 1, 2016 at 10 a.m. online. Goodyear Ballpark Ticket Office opens January 14, 2017 at 10 a.m. Schedule and ticket info for Cincinnati Reds Cactus League games 
When do the Colorado Rockies Spring Training tickets go on sale? January 7, 2017 at 10 a.m. online, at the box office at Salt River Fields at Talking Stick or by calling 1-888-490-0383. Schedule and ticket info for Colorado Rockies Cactus League games 
When do the Kansas City Royals Spring Training tickets go on sale? December 10, 2016 at 8 a.m. online and by phone. The box office opens on January 7, 2017 at 7 a.m. 
When do the Chicago White Sox Spring Training tickets go on sale? January 9, 2017 by phone and online. Box office opens January 30, 2017 at 10 a.m.
